WEBVTT

01:52.120 --> 01:57.570
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.620 --> 02:01.930
[Episode 13]

02:29.000 --> 02:30.150
What's on your mind?

02:33.540 --> 02:35.510
You seem out of it.

02:35.540 --> 02:37.670
Is the Commerce Bureau that grueling?

02:42.840 --> 02:44.030
No.

02:45.400 --> 02:46.910
It's because

02:47.960 --> 02:49.110
my mother

02:49.690 --> 02:51.600
also passed away

02:52.560 --> 02:54.670
on a stormy summer night like this.

03:02.710 --> 03:04.970
Her death anniversary is coming up soon.

03:06.730 --> 03:08.570
Every year around this time,

03:08.600 --> 03:10.520
my dad stays indoors

03:10.540 --> 03:12.060
and won't visit her grave.

03:13.490 --> 03:15.260
But I know

03:15.630 --> 03:17.160
he's just afraid to go;

03:18.400 --> 03:20.660
afraid of losing control of his emotions

03:21.079 --> 03:22.970
and afraid of feeling sad.

03:29.150 --> 03:30.190
So,

03:30.400 --> 03:31.990
I was just thinking about

03:32.010 --> 03:33.490
how to comfort him

03:33.520 --> 03:35.290
when I get home later.

03:37.610 --> 03:38.720
That's why

03:39.760 --> 03:41.220
you're scared of thunder.

03:48.200 --> 03:49.920
Not only do I hate thunder,

03:50.780 --> 03:52.440
but I also really hate summer.

03:59.650 --> 04:00.530
How about

04:01.110 --> 04:02.840
I go with you to visit her grave?

04:08.020 --> 04:09.190
After all,

04:10.840 --> 04:12.500
we were once husband and wife.

04:22.980 --> 04:30.170
[Fan Residence]

04:35.950 --> 04:37.280
You can drop me off here.

04:37.590 --> 04:38.740
After all...

04:40.450 --> 04:42.570
Besides, if my dad sees us,

04:42.600 --> 04:44.659
he'll start imagining things again.

04:46.159 --> 04:47.070
Alright then.

04:48.680 --> 04:50.010
Take this umbrella.

04:51.870 --> 04:53.120
-But you…
-I'm fine.

04:54.800 --> 04:55.530
Go inside.

05:48.980 --> 05:49.630
Fan Yun.

05:51.920 --> 05:53.440
Why are you still up?

05:54.050 --> 05:55.450
I was going to pick you up,

05:55.770 --> 05:56.680
but

05:57.070 --> 05:58.270
you're already back.

06:01.960 --> 06:03.400
A friend walked me back.

06:06.750 --> 06:08.310
I'm relieved you have
someone to keep you company

06:08.310 --> 06:09.510
on a stormy night.

06:11.650 --> 06:13.680
I thought you'd look all miserable.

06:14.220 --> 06:17.750
I guess working at the Commerce Bureau
helps lift your spirits.

06:19.270 --> 06:19.830
Gao Ran.

06:22.270 --> 06:23.720
I think

06:24.950 --> 06:27.310
I don't hate summer as much anymore.

06:29.740 --> 06:31.300
Maybe like them,

06:32.110 --> 06:33.390
I have

06:34.390 --> 06:36.050
new expectations for summer.

06:59.690 --> 07:01.730
I really like the sound of that.

07:03.360 --> 07:05.980
Unc... Uncle?

07:23.570 --> 07:26.800
Say, Fan Yun really is exceptional,
isn't she?

07:32.200 --> 07:34.770
You've been visiting my Commerce Bureau
a lot lately.

07:34.770 --> 07:36.909
Lord Fan, it's just an excuse
to see your niece,

07:36.909 --> 07:37.720
isn't it?

07:42.120 --> 07:42.970
As expected,

07:43.000 --> 07:44.570
you knew that

07:45.120 --> 07:46.530
she's my niece all along.

07:48.970 --> 07:50.600
Why are you saying this now?

07:51.110 --> 07:53.440
Are you actually trying to drive her away?

07:54.390 --> 07:57.450
If I hadn't witnessed her proficiency
with my own eyes,

07:57.670 --> 08:00.270
in spite of her
having the governor's backing,

08:00.680 --> 08:02.290
I'd have a million ways

08:02.870 --> 08:04.190
to make her back down.

08:07.390 --> 08:10.080
However, this doesn't mean
I agree with the governor

08:10.080 --> 08:11.600
hastily implementing

08:12.060 --> 08:13.600
reforms to the exam system.

08:14.240 --> 08:17.300
The ingrained prejudice that
only men can be officials

08:17.870 --> 08:20.750
can't be eradicated overnight.

08:21.830 --> 08:22.420
I agree.

08:23.270 --> 08:24.870
As the head of the Fan family,

08:24.870 --> 08:27.430
I bear a responsibility
to the noble faction.

08:28.660 --> 08:30.130
He has his reasons,

08:30.660 --> 08:32.370
and I have my objections.

08:33.720 --> 08:35.679
I do not compromise on matters

08:36.390 --> 08:37.530
of principles.

08:42.669 --> 08:43.559
However,

08:44.270 --> 08:45.670
I have another question.

08:47.230 --> 08:49.060
You're always so stern and grim

08:49.660 --> 08:52.120
that even ghosts
despair at the sight of you.

08:53.280 --> 08:55.560
She called you Uncle just once,

08:56.840 --> 08:58.060
and you became

08:58.960 --> 09:02.000
so radiant and joyful

09:03.180 --> 09:05.930
that even my mask couldn't hide it.

09:06.980 --> 09:09.180
Since you care so much about your niece,

09:09.720 --> 09:12.380
why not just reconcile
with your older brother?

09:14.760 --> 09:16.060
Easy for you to say.

09:19.150 --> 09:20.410
As the old saying goes,

09:20.750 --> 09:22.610
an elder brother is like a father.

09:22.780 --> 09:24.230
But back then,

09:24.250 --> 09:25.560
for that Ji Qiangwei,

09:26.060 --> 09:28.670
Yun's father gave up
the position of family head,

09:28.670 --> 09:29.630
which pushed me

09:29.630 --> 09:31.560
into an irreversible dead end.

09:33.480 --> 09:36.200
So why should I reconcile

09:36.200 --> 09:37.540
with him now?

09:39.360 --> 09:40.560
Enough talking.

09:43.290 --> 09:44.250
Right.

09:45.150 --> 09:47.000
Here is a new mask for you.

09:47.250 --> 09:50.360
I personally think it suits you very well.

10:02.960 --> 10:04.000
It's so ugly.

10:04.500 --> 10:05.590
I won't wear it!

10:29.510 --> 10:30.770
Your handiwork skills

10:31.170 --> 10:33.300
were all taught by your mother, right?

10:34.680 --> 10:35.650
The opposite.

10:37.070 --> 10:38.540
When my mother was alive,

10:38.770 --> 10:39.800
just like my dad,

10:40.060 --> 10:42.120
she was not cut out for delicate work.

10:42.550 --> 10:43.960
Instead, things like

10:43.980 --> 10:45.170
climbing trees

10:45.200 --> 10:46.370
and picking fruits,

10:46.390 --> 10:47.590
she was quite good at.

10:50.630 --> 10:52.830
So you inherited your mother's legacy.

10:56.530 --> 10:58.590
I don't have my mother's good health.

10:59.420 --> 11:01.220
I've always been frail and sick,

11:01.400 --> 11:02.730
taking medicine daily.

11:05.170 --> 11:06.170
You're frail?

11:17.640 --> 11:19.640
It wasn't until I grew up a bit

11:20.370 --> 11:21.400
that my health

11:22.030 --> 11:23.960
improved little by little.

11:28.810 --> 11:29.920
Maybe

11:30.160 --> 11:31.390
it really was me

11:32.250 --> 11:34.110
who ruined my mother's health.

12:07.220 --> 12:08.180
Tell me;

12:09.360 --> 12:11.890
why is it that
the closer you get to your dream,

12:12.490 --> 12:14.100
the more unsure

12:14.560 --> 12:16.100
you feel?

12:19.480 --> 12:20.510
You mean

12:21.150 --> 12:22.680
advocating for the people?

12:28.120 --> 12:29.270
Anyway,

12:29.960 --> 12:32.110
in my time in the Commerce Bureau,

12:32.790 --> 12:35.080
I always feel like I'm not doing enough.

12:40.120 --> 12:41.720
Only when you're incredibly close,

12:41.720 --> 12:43.520
yet still a hair's breadth away,

12:43.960 --> 12:46.420
do you start to
worry about gains and losses.

12:49.520 --> 12:51.520
Worry about gains and losses...

12:55.070 --> 12:57.250
Yes, that's the feeling,

12:57.670 --> 12:59.530
worrying about gains and losses.

12:59.750 --> 13:01.000
The harder you want to try,

13:01.000 --> 13:02.400
the more you fear losing.

13:02.750 --> 13:04.020
Then you want to try harder,

13:04.020 --> 13:05.120
even harder,

13:05.630 --> 13:08.030
to do everything perfectly.

13:10.270 --> 13:11.730
But I believe you can do it.

13:18.360 --> 13:19.510
Look at yourself.

13:20.000 --> 13:21.880
Burning the midnight oil every night,

13:21.880 --> 13:24.080
the stack of documents towers over you.

13:25.030 --> 13:27.130
Always skipping meals and losing sleep.

13:27.130 --> 13:28.350
When given work,

13:28.720 --> 13:30.440
others complain endlessly,

13:30.680 --> 13:31.530
but you

13:32.000 --> 13:33.270
actually enjoy it.

13:35.730 --> 13:36.310
Wait,

13:36.720 --> 13:38.250
how do you know everything?

13:38.570 --> 13:40.050
Who am I?

13:40.080 --> 13:41.360
I'm the governor.

14:06.800 --> 14:07.760
Sure, sure.

14:07.790 --> 14:08.940
You're the governor;

14:08.940 --> 14:09.870
you're amazing;

14:09.880 --> 14:11.610
you know everything, alright?

14:14.440 --> 14:15.270
Fan Yun,

14:16.610 --> 14:19.280
this exam reform is unprecedented.

14:20.020 --> 14:21.550
It's also our first battle.

14:22.380 --> 14:23.580
Even as the governor,

14:23.800 --> 14:25.400
I'm not entirely confident.

14:26.330 --> 14:27.820
So it's understandable that

14:27.820 --> 14:29.030
you have concerns.

14:30.010 --> 14:31.040
But it's fine.

14:31.890 --> 14:33.750
Who says worry prevents success?

14:35.170 --> 14:37.300
Just accept your momentary weakness,

14:37.720 --> 14:39.150
then go all out together

14:39.550 --> 14:40.670
and step forward.

14:46.000 --> 14:47.600
Aren't all grand goals

14:48.270 --> 14:50.390
achieved step by step like this?

14:51.910 --> 14:53.170
Let's both do our best.

14:53.880 --> 14:54.740
Do you trust me?

15:06.030 --> 15:06.960
I trust you.

15:42.860 --> 15:43.860
Young Master Shi.

15:45.030 --> 15:45.870
Uncle Yi.

15:45.980 --> 15:47.040
Don't knock yet.

15:47.310 --> 15:48.910
Let Master rest a bit longer.

15:50.670 --> 15:52.390
Is Grandfather feeling unwell?

15:52.390 --> 15:53.560
It's already so late.

15:53.560 --> 15:55.080
He never sleeps in.

15:55.630 --> 15:57.550
You don't know this, but last night,

15:57.550 --> 15:59.030
Master sat in the pavilion

15:59.030 --> 16:00.080
until dawn,

16:00.230 --> 16:01.670
and even skipped breakfast.

16:01.670 --> 16:03.080
He just went in to rest.

16:03.680 --> 16:05.630
What kept Grandfather awake all night?

16:05.630 --> 16:06.750
Master didn't say,

16:06.770 --> 16:08.100
and I didn't dare to ask.

16:08.680 --> 16:10.210
I just heard Master mention

16:11.240 --> 16:12.900
the national selection exam.

16:16.340 --> 16:17.050
Grandfather.

16:17.050 --> 16:21.050
Our Zheng family has been the pillar
of the Nine Cities for generations.

16:21.120 --> 16:22.610
I absolutely won't allow such a thing

16:22.610 --> 16:24.610
to happen under my watch!

16:25.940 --> 16:27.300
Although I'm old,

16:27.320 --> 16:28.560
I'm still alive and kicking.

16:28.560 --> 16:30.060
As long as I have a breath in me,

16:30.060 --> 16:31.980
I'll never let him run wild!

16:32.600 --> 16:33.480
To his estate!

17:01.120 --> 17:02.780
Greetings, Your Excellency.

17:05.440 --> 17:06.480
Lord Jiang,

17:07.180 --> 17:09.780
has Fan Xiu been of help
at the Commerce Bureau?

17:09.839 --> 17:11.369
She's highly intelligent.

17:11.440 --> 17:13.040
During her time in my bureau,

17:13.069 --> 17:14.589
she has indeed done a lot.

17:18.960 --> 17:20.550
Then do you think

17:20.960 --> 17:22.290
women can be officials?

17:24.349 --> 17:26.270
Your Excellency, are you trying to

17:26.270 --> 17:28.470
ask about the national selection exam?

17:30.750 --> 17:32.010
I must say, Lord Jiang,

17:32.570 --> 17:34.030
you're truly impressive;

17:34.390 --> 17:35.860
great at reading between the lines.

17:35.860 --> 17:37.990
Nothing can be hidden from you indeed.

17:38.310 --> 17:39.650
Regarding this matter,

17:40.030 --> 17:41.110
I neither approve

17:41.660 --> 17:42.700
nor oppose it.

17:43.150 --> 17:45.080
That doesn't sound like you at all.

17:46.030 --> 17:47.400
In my opinion,

17:48.000 --> 17:48.880
this matter has

17:49.400 --> 17:51.310
gone beyond the exam itself.

17:52.110 --> 17:53.370
The root of the problem

17:54.030 --> 17:56.360
lies in the foundation of the Nine Cities.

17:56.830 --> 17:57.920
Do you think

17:58.170 --> 17:59.770
I'm shaking the foundation?

18:00.750 --> 18:01.970
It is not me,

18:02.440 --> 18:04.510
but the Nine Noble Families.

18:05.160 --> 18:06.610
This has already become

18:06.820 --> 18:08.020
a factional dispute.

18:08.440 --> 18:11.680
At the upper level, it compromises
the unity of the Nine Cities.

18:11.680 --> 18:15.740
At the lower level, it jeopardizes
the livelihoods of the common people.

18:16.200 --> 18:17.530
And the last thing I want

18:17.920 --> 18:19.530
is to get involved in these

18:19.560 --> 18:20.840
factional disputes.

18:21.680 --> 18:24.960
So you're just looking out for yourself
and want to stay out of it?

18:24.960 --> 18:26.720
I haven't settled the score with you
for unethically

18:26.720 --> 18:27.550
deceiving a patient!

18:27.550 --> 18:29.110
Didn't Your Excellency say this matter

18:29.110 --> 18:30.160
was written off?

18:30.160 --> 18:31.750
Well, that matter can be written off,

18:31.750 --> 18:32.640
but I can...

18:33.160 --> 18:35.390
punish you for secretly accepting
a woman into your bureau!

18:35.390 --> 18:37.370
Please don't joke, Your Excellency.

18:37.370 --> 18:38.360
Fan Yun was

18:38.590 --> 18:40.030
forced upon me by Your Excellency.

18:40.030 --> 18:40.670
You...

18:44.570 --> 18:45.160
Fine.

18:45.850 --> 18:47.910
I can spare you from a heavy sentence.

18:48.510 --> 18:50.270
I'll punish you by forbidding you

18:50.270 --> 18:51.510
from wearing a mask.

18:52.110 --> 18:54.370
You must show your actual face in public.

18:55.880 --> 18:56.750
How about it?

18:57.680 --> 18:59.940
Think it through carefully, Lord Jia...

19:06.920 --> 19:08.480
Changing your mask means

19:08.500 --> 19:09.460
you agree?

19:11.530 --> 19:12.920
If you agree,

19:13.830 --> 19:15.560
it'll be much easier to handle.

19:32.870 --> 19:34.140
Fan Yun?

19:38.600 --> 19:39.890
Fan Yun.

19:43.350 --> 19:44.980
W-What Fan Yun?

19:45.000 --> 19:46.170
Who's Fan Yun?

19:46.480 --> 19:47.790
I... I'm not Fan Yun.

19:47.790 --> 19:48.480
Stop.

19:48.480 --> 19:49.200
I'm not Fan Yun.

19:49.200 --> 19:50.240
Stop right there!

20:33.700 --> 20:34.500
Fan Yun.

20:35.990 --> 20:37.050
What are you doing?

20:37.120 --> 20:38.640
You scared me to death.

20:38.660 --> 20:40.660
-You scared me.
-What are you doing?

20:42.150 --> 20:43.480
I... I...

20:44.720 --> 20:46.070
Nothing.

20:46.090 --> 20:46.730
By the way,

20:46.960 --> 20:48.230
I was looking for Gao Ran,

20:48.230 --> 20:49.250
but he wasn't home.

20:49.250 --> 20:50.520
Do you know where he went?

20:50.520 --> 20:51.930
Gao Ran?

20:53.250 --> 20:54.860
Since he resigned,

20:54.890 --> 20:56.960
he's taken over all the housework.

20:57.680 --> 20:59.270
At this hour, he should be

20:59.800 --> 21:01.380
at the market buying groceries.

21:01.380 --> 21:02.390
Buying groceries?

21:02.390 --> 21:03.320
Then I'll go too.

21:04.170 --> 21:05.500
What's the rush?

21:06.040 --> 21:06.880
I'm free after

21:06.900 --> 21:09.480
delivering these documents
to the Rites Bureau.

21:09.480 --> 21:10.640
How about you

21:10.670 --> 21:11.610
wait for me

21:12.110 --> 21:13.630
and go home with me after?

21:13.650 --> 21:14.890
Go home with you?

21:15.710 --> 21:16.910
Where Gao Ran will be?

21:17.030 --> 21:17.880
Let's go!

21:18.470 --> 21:19.100
Let's go.

21:19.250 --> 21:21.800
"The upcoming selection-exam reform
will be repealed.

21:21.800 --> 21:24.860
Nobles are invited to participate
in the discussion."

21:32.120 --> 21:34.320
Lord Zheng Yuan requests an audience!

21:41.700 --> 21:42.440
Elder Zheng!

21:45.510 --> 21:47.310
Why do you look so pale?

21:47.340 --> 21:47.830
Come,

21:48.190 --> 21:49.150
please sit.

21:50.890 --> 21:52.160
Dont worry about

21:52.180 --> 21:53.040
my health.

21:56.900 --> 21:58.120
Then you're...

21:58.590 --> 21:59.830
Your Excellency,

22:00.030 --> 22:02.160
since yesterday's morning assembly,

22:02.180 --> 22:03.710
I have been thinking a lot.

22:04.720 --> 22:06.290
Back then, the late governor

22:06.290 --> 22:08.060
entrusted you to me.

22:09.640 --> 22:10.830
I'm afraid

22:11.830 --> 22:13.960
I've disappointed him.

22:15.700 --> 22:17.370
Aren't I doing well?

22:19.700 --> 22:20.560
I don't mean...

22:20.820 --> 22:22.090
I don't mean your dysfunction!

22:22.090 --> 22:24.190
My dysfunction has nothing to do with you.

22:24.190 --> 22:26.050
I've been taking my medicine on time
as you instructed,

22:26.050 --> 22:27.230
so don't worry.

22:27.480 --> 22:28.810
Is there anything else?

22:29.060 --> 22:30.740
In the estate's garden,

22:32.160 --> 22:33.620
Your Excellency proposed

22:34.080 --> 22:36.340
opening the selection exam to everyone,

22:36.520 --> 22:38.280
which caused a huge uproar.

22:40.550 --> 22:41.920
I think

22:42.720 --> 22:43.650
Your Excellency

22:44.510 --> 22:47.110
should give up this idea.

22:49.550 --> 22:51.310
Oh, you're talking about this.

22:51.390 --> 22:52.930
I did think about it after.

22:53.640 --> 22:54.970
I was indeed impulsive.

22:55.290 --> 22:56.800
If you hadn't stopped me in time,

22:56.800 --> 22:59.060
I'd have made a huge mistake, wouldn't I?

23:00.290 --> 23:02.640
Do you truly mean that, Your Excellency?

23:02.750 --> 23:03.640
Absolutely.

23:08.480 --> 23:11.680
Then... I have nothing more to say.

23:12.100 --> 23:13.410
I'll take my leave.

23:15.730 --> 23:16.530
Wait...

23:18.360 --> 23:19.670
Today,

23:20.430 --> 23:22.560
I saw a familiar figure in the estate.

23:24.110 --> 23:25.070
It looked like

23:25.550 --> 23:26.480
Fan Yun.

23:27.920 --> 23:29.540
Your Excellency, are you

23:30.200 --> 23:31.800
hiding Fan Yun in the estate?

23:32.350 --> 23:33.480
Fan Yun?

23:34.110 --> 23:35.200
She's back? Where?

23:37.200 --> 23:38.200
Why didn't I know?

23:40.000 --> 23:40.730
Elder Zheng,

23:41.520 --> 23:43.200
are you sure your health is OK?

23:43.220 --> 23:44.480
You're seeing things!

23:44.800 --> 23:46.360
If I wanted Fan Yun here,

23:46.390 --> 23:47.930
why would I have divorced her?

23:47.930 --> 23:48.690
Right?

23:50.820 --> 23:52.100
That's true.

23:54.290 --> 23:55.360
Makes sense.

24:00.400 --> 24:01.400
Your Excellency,

24:01.790 --> 24:02.770
I am

24:03.250 --> 24:05.250
fully dedicated to the Nine Cities.

24:05.670 --> 24:07.070
I hope Your Excellency is

24:07.310 --> 24:09.400
fully dedicated to our cause as well.

24:11.120 --> 24:12.230
Of course.

24:13.110 --> 24:13.970
I shall

24:14.160 --> 24:15.200
take my leave.

24:18.930 --> 24:20.390
I should take my medicine!

24:50.670 --> 24:53.120
So Fan Hui really made you call him Uncle?

24:55.480 --> 24:56.770
If you ask me, there is

24:56.810 --> 24:59.410
really no shortage of oddballs
in this estate.

25:00.880 --> 25:01.830
Do you think

25:02.270 --> 25:04.020
he... he might have

25:04.430 --> 25:06.430
figured out my real identity?

25:08.010 --> 25:09.050
If you ask me,

25:09.080 --> 25:10.820
Fan Yun, you're effortlessly beautiful.

25:10.820 --> 25:13.150
Even men's clothes can't hide your charm.

25:13.230 --> 25:14.230
This won't do.

25:15.980 --> 25:17.680
Why don't I teach you some self-defense

25:17.680 --> 25:19.280
so you can protect yourself?

25:19.830 --> 25:20.960
You?

25:20.960 --> 25:21.680
Teach me?

25:21.680 --> 25:22.960
What do you mean by that?

25:22.960 --> 25:23.460
Don't believe me?

25:23.460 --> 25:24.660
Then I'll show you...

25:34.750 --> 25:35.470
Fan Yun.

25:35.490 --> 25:36.960
It turns out you

25:36.990 --> 25:38.880
have formidable strength.

25:38.900 --> 25:39.800
N-No, no.

25:40.110 --> 25:41.240
I really didn't mean to.

25:41.240 --> 25:42.170
This... This...

25:42.570 --> 25:43.870
Miss Wei, don't bother.

25:43.870 --> 25:45.330
You might prick your hand.

25:45.560 --> 25:46.470
The table...

25:47.440 --> 25:49.570
Our tables are always like this.

25:49.600 --> 25:50.860
I'll just fix it later.

25:56.010 --> 25:57.140
Living in

25:57.170 --> 25:58.890
such a shabby place?

25:59.720 --> 26:00.850
It's fine. I'm fine.

26:00.870 --> 26:02.870
Suffering so much.

26:02.920 --> 26:04.030
I'm not suffering.

26:04.030 --> 26:05.330
Don't worry, Miss Wei.

26:05.350 --> 26:06.430
But

26:06.920 --> 26:08.140
my Gao Ran

26:08.480 --> 26:09.760
is so pitiful!

26:11.790 --> 26:13.790
I thought you were worried about me.

26:15.780 --> 26:17.240
I'm worried about you too.

26:18.310 --> 26:18.970
Alright.

26:19.030 --> 26:21.000
Teach me a few self-defense moves then.

26:21.000 --> 26:21.490
Sure.

26:22.950 --> 26:23.670
Come on.

26:25.590 --> 26:26.270
Attack me.

26:27.950 --> 26:28.880
Attack you?

26:29.610 --> 26:30.290
Where...

26:30.310 --> 26:31.290
Where should I hit?

26:31.290 --> 26:31.850
Just hit

26:31.870 --> 26:32.590
here!

26:33.000 --> 26:33.800
-Here?
-Here.

26:35.490 --> 26:36.160
Move.

26:36.200 --> 26:36.710
Twist.

26:38.020 --> 26:38.630
Grab.

26:39.310 --> 26:40.170
And then you...

26:40.440 --> 26:41.000
Stop!

26:59.720 --> 27:00.630
What were you up to?

27:00.630 --> 27:01.670
Nothing!

27:02.030 --> 27:03.630
You misunderstood, Gao Ran.

27:03.930 --> 27:06.130
Miss Wei was teaching me self-defense.

27:06.310 --> 27:07.260
Self-defense?

27:10.600 --> 27:11.430
Wait, wait!

27:11.450 --> 27:12.570
You didn't misunderstand.

27:12.570 --> 27:14.170
Quick, grab me and arrest me.

27:20.830 --> 27:21.660
Gao Ran.

27:23.290 --> 27:24.240
Gao Ran.

27:24.270 --> 27:26.130
You said you liked me being noisy.

27:26.140 --> 27:27.800
How about it? Do you like this?

27:28.600 --> 27:29.710
Did I say that?

27:29.730 --> 27:30.490
You did.

27:31.160 --> 27:32.160
I'm going to cook.

27:32.280 --> 27:33.000
Gao Ran.

27:34.030 --> 27:35.000
Why not

27:35.290 --> 27:37.530
have Miss Wei stay for dinner?

27:38.560 --> 27:39.920
Gao Ran can cook?

27:41.040 --> 27:41.990
Let me eat!

27:59.560 --> 28:01.760
Gao Ran's cooking is really delicious.

28:02.320 --> 28:04.450
This must be the best food in the world.

28:05.830 --> 28:06.480
Um,

28:06.530 --> 28:07.450
you two eat.

28:07.540 --> 28:09.470
I'll go deliver food to Lord Fan Qi.

28:10.280 --> 28:10.930
Gao Ran,

28:10.960 --> 28:12.030
are you leaving?

28:13.180 --> 28:14.000
Why don't

28:14.370 --> 28:15.830
I go deliver food to my dad?

28:16.410 --> 28:17.470
As for you, Gao Ran,

28:17.560 --> 28:19.320
just stay here

28:19.400 --> 28:21.090
and have a meal with Miss Wei.

28:22.750 --> 28:23.350
I'm off.

28:24.400 --> 28:25.110
Fan Yun!

28:26.230 --> 28:28.090
Didn't you hear what Fan Yun said?

28:28.720 --> 28:29.990
Fan Yun said

28:30.220 --> 28:31.620
to keep Miss Wei company.

28:39.530 --> 28:40.200
Eat.

28:40.540 --> 28:41.230
Let's eat.

28:43.200 --> 28:43.920
Dad.

28:44.900 --> 28:46.290
I brought you food.

28:47.550 --> 28:48.270
It's Yun

28:48.270 --> 28:49.960
bringing me food today!

28:51.040 --> 28:52.470
Wonderful.

28:52.490 --> 28:53.440
You must be starving.

28:53.440 --> 28:54.000
I am!

28:54.020 --> 28:56.750
It's been a long time
since I tasted your cooking.

28:57.830 --> 28:58.790
Come on!

28:58.790 --> 28:59.640
Quick.

28:59.700 --> 29:01.230
Let me set the table for you.

29:08.370 --> 29:10.130
You know what?

29:10.150 --> 29:12.380
The food Gao Ran makes

29:12.780 --> 29:14.340
is horrible.

29:25.480 --> 29:26.640
Is it horrible?

29:28.510 --> 29:29.640
Yun.

29:29.670 --> 29:32.010
Have you been too tired and busy lately?

29:32.190 --> 29:33.600
I mean,

29:33.630 --> 29:34.700
the food...

29:35.440 --> 29:36.280
Dad.

29:36.310 --> 29:38.160
Actually, this meal today

29:38.200 --> 29:40.070
was made by Gao Ran.

29:40.580 --> 29:41.730
But I packed the food

29:41.760 --> 29:43.650
into this food box myself.

29:44.470 --> 29:45.800
No wonder t-today's...

29:45.820 --> 29:46.580
today's food

29:46.610 --> 29:47.450
is so good!

29:47.480 --> 29:49.160
Food packed by my little girl

29:49.160 --> 29:50.310
sure is different.

29:50.310 --> 29:51.310
Delicious!

29:52.200 --> 29:53.400
Yum, yum, yum.

29:54.790 --> 29:55.680
Dad.

29:55.680 --> 29:57.040
When I'm less busy,

29:57.250 --> 29:59.060
I promise I'll cook a fantastic meal

29:59.060 --> 30:00.780
to pamper you.

30:05.300 --> 30:07.260
Don't you placate me.

30:07.290 --> 30:08.480
Look,

30:08.590 --> 30:10.590
after you finish with the Commerce Bureau,

30:10.590 --> 30:12.780
you'll have to
take the selection exam, right?

30:12.780 --> 30:15.980
After the exam,
you'll take up an official post.

30:16.590 --> 30:17.310
Am I right?

30:17.790 --> 30:18.790
In the future,

30:18.790 --> 30:20.750
I doubt I'll ever get to eat

30:21.400 --> 30:22.400
the food you cook.

30:23.510 --> 30:26.070
I can make time to cook for you, Dad.

30:28.650 --> 30:29.540
Yun.

30:30.340 --> 30:31.230
Well,

30:31.640 --> 30:34.410
many people in the estate are against

30:34.680 --> 30:36.570
the governor's reform policies.

30:37.310 --> 30:39.810
Your odds of taking the selection exam

30:40.200 --> 30:41.010
aren't high.

30:45.160 --> 30:46.960
I know who you're talking about.

30:47.750 --> 30:49.570
Lord Zheng is really something,

30:49.730 --> 30:51.660
opposing the governor to his face.

30:52.180 --> 30:53.420
I bet he's the only one

30:53.450 --> 30:55.250
in this estate who would do that.

30:56.010 --> 30:57.040
There is another one!

30:57.040 --> 30:58.970
He's even fiercer than Lord Zheng.

30:59.440 --> 31:00.810
Another one?

31:00.830 --> 31:01.520
Who is it?

31:08.280 --> 31:09.120
Fan Hui!

31:11.580 --> 31:13.860
Fan Hui is my biological uncle?

31:37.230 --> 31:38.830
-Fan Yun!
-Your Excellency!

31:39.310 --> 31:40.290
Why are you here?

31:40.310 --> 31:41.340
You found me.

31:41.730 --> 31:42.290
Come on.

31:42.510 --> 31:44.180
Let's go do something important.

31:44.180 --> 31:44.980
Where to?

31:45.000 --> 31:46.530
I still have guests at home.

31:47.030 --> 31:48.030
Just come with me.

31:48.050 --> 31:49.650
-Hurry.
-Where are we going?

31:51.040 --> 31:51.770
Lord Fan,

31:52.310 --> 31:53.640
have some more to drink.

31:54.350 --> 31:55.260
No thanks.

31:55.780 --> 31:56.840
It's getting late.

31:57.200 --> 31:57.920
Goodbye.

31:59.200 --> 32:00.310
Lord Fan!

32:03.320 --> 32:04.280
Your Excellency.

32:04.280 --> 32:05.280
Your Excellency.

32:06.240 --> 32:07.700
Have you thought about it?

32:11.220 --> 32:12.170
Your Excellency,

32:12.170 --> 32:14.650
I cannot obey this order.

32:16.200 --> 32:17.920
I have my own principles.

32:17.950 --> 32:19.000
Principles

32:19.430 --> 32:20.560
cannot be violated.

32:21.240 --> 32:23.510
I'm the governor of the Nine Cities
after all,

32:23.510 --> 32:25.240
but you won't even
give me this much respect.

32:25.240 --> 32:28.040
Aren't you afraid
I'll dismiss you from your post?

32:30.160 --> 32:32.670
It is easy
for Your Excellency to dismiss me.

32:33.040 --> 32:34.200
But

32:34.270 --> 32:35.790
to make me obey is

32:36.590 --> 32:37.400
impossible.

32:37.400 --> 32:37.960
You...

32:39.270 --> 32:40.070
Just you wait.

32:40.480 --> 32:41.440
Uncle.

32:46.590 --> 32:47.310
I'm Fan Yun.

32:47.330 --> 32:48.390
Greetings, Uncle.

32:53.350 --> 32:54.390
Fan Yun,

32:55.550 --> 32:56.680
are you really aware

32:57.500 --> 32:58.780
that I'm your uncle?

33:01.870 --> 33:04.260
I've always been your niece.

33:04.280 --> 33:05.440
Such a blood tie

33:05.470 --> 33:06.840
can never be severed.

33:07.910 --> 33:09.000
Absolutely.

33:09.600 --> 33:12.060
Blood ties can never be severed.

33:14.180 --> 33:15.140
I still remember

33:15.170 --> 33:16.310
when you were little,

33:16.310 --> 33:17.000
I used to

33:17.020 --> 33:18.660
hold you all the time.

33:23.190 --> 33:24.430
Uncle.

33:25.140 --> 33:26.690
I have a favor

33:26.720 --> 33:27.930
to ask of you.

33:28.610 --> 33:29.530
Just say it.

33:29.550 --> 33:30.910
If I can help,

33:30.940 --> 33:32.000
I definitely will.

33:32.150 --> 33:34.080
Could you support the exam reform?

33:40.480 --> 33:41.550
Well...

33:44.040 --> 33:45.480
I...

33:50.330 --> 33:54.020
-If you don't agree...
-Fan Yun.

33:54.630 --> 33:55.840
Whatever you need,

33:55.860 --> 33:56.780
I will

33:56.810 --> 33:57.810
definitely help.

34:02.590 --> 34:03.310
Your Excellency,

34:03.310 --> 34:03.790
how about this?

34:03.790 --> 34:05.140
I'll return to the estate with you

34:05.140 --> 34:05.670
right now

34:05.680 --> 34:07.210
to hear your detailed plan.

34:12.920 --> 34:14.350
Why are you just staring at me?

34:14.350 --> 34:15.190
Let's go!

34:21.340 --> 34:22.300
W-What...

34:22.330 --> 34:23.389
What about his principles?

34:23.389 --> 34:25.650
One "Uncle" and his principles are gone.

34:25.710 --> 34:26.639
But this is good.

34:26.960 --> 34:27.440
Fan Yun.

34:28.230 --> 34:29.889
I'll have to leave this to you.

34:30.100 --> 34:31.290
Go and take good care of our guest.

34:31.290 --> 34:32.090
Leave the rest

34:32.260 --> 34:33.130
to me.

34:43.360 --> 34:44.070
Gao Ran.

34:44.520 --> 34:45.920
You're such a great cook.

34:46.300 --> 34:47.699
Can I have another bowl?

34:48.480 --> 34:49.540
There's none left.

34:49.710 --> 34:50.920
It was supposed to be for dinner,

34:50.920 --> 34:52.090
but you ate it all.

34:52.449 --> 34:54.449
Miss Wei, if you've eaten your fill,

34:54.560 --> 34:55.560
you should leave.

34:55.840 --> 34:57.310
Being alone in a room with a man

34:57.310 --> 34:59.040
will tarnish your reputation.

35:01.590 --> 35:02.670
I'm not afraid.

35:03.040 --> 35:04.300
What are you afraid of?

35:04.450 --> 35:06.000
I... I'll stay a little longer.

35:06.000 --> 35:07.330
I'm in no rush to go back.

35:09.770 --> 35:10.330
You...

35:10.360 --> 35:12.090
Give me a second to digest this,

35:12.190 --> 35:12.800
and...

35:13.940 --> 35:15.070
and let's chat more,

35:15.250 --> 35:16.190
just like we did the other day.

35:16.190 --> 35:17.520
Is there anything else?

35:19.680 --> 35:20.470
I...

35:21.410 --> 35:22.450
There is.

35:22.480 --> 35:23.770
Of course there is.

35:27.170 --> 35:28.000
Then tell me.

35:32.710 --> 35:33.800
Why...

35:34.320 --> 35:36.000
are you so good-looking?

35:36.910 --> 35:37.880
Gao Ran,

35:38.430 --> 35:39.760
sometimes

35:40.050 --> 35:41.180
you feel so far away,

35:41.230 --> 35:42.760
and other times very close.

35:43.600 --> 35:44.860
But your handsome face

35:44.870 --> 35:45.940
never changes.

35:48.480 --> 35:49.240
Miss Wei,

35:49.690 --> 35:51.840
didn't you say
you wanted to be like Fan Yun

35:51.840 --> 35:53.640
and do everything you want to do?

35:55.260 --> 35:56.660
You remember what I said?

35:57.880 --> 35:59.070
I thought what you said

35:59.070 --> 36:00.100
was from the heart.

36:00.100 --> 36:01.580
It was from the heart.

36:01.610 --> 36:03.030
What I want to do the most right now

36:03.030 --> 36:05.030
is to see the person I like every day.

36:06.630 --> 36:08.620
There are plenty of good-looking men.

36:08.620 --> 36:09.310
If that is

36:09.330 --> 36:11.370
your only criterion for judgment,

36:11.400 --> 36:12.660
it's too superficial.

36:14.370 --> 36:16.770
I told you you don't understand women.

36:16.800 --> 36:17.510
You know

36:17.530 --> 36:19.130
nothing about love.

36:19.190 --> 36:21.280
How do you know
the fondness I talk about is

36:21.280 --> 36:23.340
just about superficial appearance?

36:23.630 --> 36:25.200
And how can you be sure that

36:25.560 --> 36:26.920
my praise for your looks

36:27.400 --> 36:29.360
isn't because of a fateful destiny

36:29.380 --> 36:31.030
that determines where my heart goes?

36:31.030 --> 36:33.130
You're so concerned about
whether I like you for your looks

36:33.130 --> 36:34.280
or your inner self.

36:34.680 --> 36:36.630
Does it mean you also...

36:38.230 --> 36:39.360
Miss Wei, you should

36:40.510 --> 36:41.510
really head back.

36:41.960 --> 36:43.020
I'm not finished.

36:53.310 --> 36:54.020
Fan Yun!

36:56.910 --> 36:58.120
I just remembered that

36:58.120 --> 37:00.000
I forgot my dad's food box, I think.

37:00.000 --> 37:00.830
You two continue.

37:00.830 --> 37:01.880
Carry on. Carry on.
